{
  "stem": "12447.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And whoever was last in the row would be the loser from the two groups facing each other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the street that we lived, it was a very quiet street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There wasn't that much traffic on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Very seldom you saw an automobile passing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But there was some automobiles crossing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And also, on the Radzyminska Street that I lived, it was a, a small railroad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We used to call it the [NON-ENGLISH], that it was going to-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't really recall exactly the destination of that railroad.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It wasn't a full-sized track of a railroad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was a narrower track that had, like, five or six cars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the commuter train would be running.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I believe it's Radzymin because the street was Radzyminska that we lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the town that this little train was going was Radzymin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That was the destination of this town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that's why I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "This little commuter train would run like once or twice a day alongside the street.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And when getting back to this game, what I tried to bring out, we played across.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And at one time, a car came out from around the corner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it just so happened that one of the kids was still crossing the street playing, trying to cut into the row of the other group.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the kid was hit by a car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I don't know the speed the car was running.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But it just happened that the kid wound up with a broken leg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Well, we just got some help.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I don't remember exactly-- the ambulance came, or whatever happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But after everybody went home, they came knocking on our door, that I was responsible for pushing this kid under the automobile.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
